OL,5,G1900 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FDocumentary series. The
OL,7,     Finterceptors of Durham and
OL,8,     FCleveland tackle a stand-off
OL,9,     Fbetween armed officers and a
OL,10,     Fdangerous knifeman and a man
OL,11,     Fwielding a length of guttering.
OL,12,G2000 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,13,G     Speeders
OL,14,     FIn Newcastle police crack down on
OL,15,     Fdrink and drug drivers and
OL,16,     Funinsured vehicles. And with lives
OL,17,     Fat risk at a crash, officers must
OL,18,     Fseparate the truth from lies.
