OL,5,G2100 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,6,G     Speeders
OL,7,     FA call about a robbery and assault
OL,8,     Fleads to a hunt on Humberside
OL,9,     Fpolice's patch with dog and drone
OL,10,     Funits. And in Scunthorpe there's a
OL,11,     Fcatastrophic road collision.
OL,12,G2200 Police Code Zero: Officer Under
OL,13,G     Attack
OL,14,     FVideo and first-hand testimony
OL,15,     Ffrom police on the front line. In
OL,16,     FNorth Wales, officers head to a
OL,17,     Fcar park, where a large group of
OL,18,     Fyoungsters appear to be drunk and
OL,19,     Farguing.
